{"tid":2217550,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"親戚幫外國床褥代工，會唔會有人有興趣？","createTime":"2020-09-25T13:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T08:10:45.000Z","uid":109453,"like":11,"dislike":84,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"262e1090dda8fd1423eaae88980b309825ecb65e","tid":2217550,"uid":109453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:48:27.000Z","msg":"話說親戚係大陸開公廠幫外國大牌子床褥做代工，連登仔吹奏果幾隻都有做，如果我自己拎黎香港賣，大家會唔會有興趣？<br />\n個價錢係香港既一半價錢以下，但就唔可以印牌子。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如我岩岩見到香港賣緊8xxx，但我拎貨都係3500連運，當我賺500，賣4000，會唔會有人有興趣？<br />\n<br />\n如果有得捻我就係香港租個場，俾大家上去試，試岩先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠100正評我就做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab524c8db5f6573ff7fd0cc29754424669e15691","tid":2217550,"uid":59911,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"夠正評先做咁唔好做"},{"pid":"1eab7fdb2c6aea86e8d437c2dd245aacc9c9d4e4","tid":2217550,"uid":115579,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"連登仔冇消費力，你諗清楚d"},{"pid":"5b4334b1d2feabb598c587e7661e4d1e0c047c89","tid":2217550,"uid":136797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:06:02.000Z","msg":"香港都有2間代購連運<br />\n你舖都冇學人做生意"},{"pid":"75e2fbedfd7904f1b2cd348b1684e0a6c71b62f4","tid":2217550,"uid":109453,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ab524c8db5f6573ff7fd0cc29754424669e15691","tid":2217550,"uid":59911,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:54:58.000Z","msg":"夠正評先做咁唔好做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"都係想知有幾多人有興趣姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027556fd134a68f4f54e66dab3da4f51779246ef","tid":2217550,"uid":42426,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:08:31.000Z","msg":"唔可以印牌子<br />\n你叫人點信你"},{"pid":"00c709fbfa03d79b16edfeb2fa84c4942